subject: Baseball
Little League World Series
lead_paragraph: Chin-Hao Yang went 4 for 4 with three runs and Kaohsiung, Taiwan, cruised in an elimination game at the Little League World Series with a 20-3 rout of Oranjestad, Aruba, in South Williamsport, Pa.
